task.summary: integration of UniProtJAPI, mapping to homologous sequences
moved to consistent handling of identifier objects and their creation via a factory
logging more consistent, creation of AminoAcids now by reflection
support for nucleotide families and prototypes
stub to create feature vectors of mutation sites
really rough implementation of structural mutation effect predictor
dropped toAtomContainer etc and standardized by toIsolatedStructure

ignores now sparsely populated modules consistent bfactor assignment for global comparability support for naming by custom contact definition schemes

adds calculation of clustering-comparison scores
naive score chi-squared coefficient

improves calculation of clustering-comparison scores
bugfixes rand index pattern to define modules added experimental module definition from literature

basic implementation of graphs
support for: graphs, edges, clusters/modules/partitions and partitioned graphs
adds weight (i.e. energy) to interaction types
fixes major bugs in generation of partition of secondary structures
some clean-up and more edge weighting schemes
stub for the ordering of modules during folding

some cleanup in CSV-generation

routine for contact tables and coupling csv
extends contact csv generation by number of observations

support for crude PDB format flaws found in CASP

stub for contacts-module and cone-peeling algorithm

parametrization of reconstruction pipeline
- adaptation for start2fold dataset
clean-up and recreation of results as constraints were swapped
